Photo, COLOR, Erik, left, and Lyle Menendez leave memorial service for their 
slain parents last August. On Thursday, 22-year-old Lyle was arrested on 
suspicion of murder; his 19-year-old brother was being sought. STEVE DYKES / 
Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Southland Edition) Jose Menendez 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
