EAST GERMANY; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; NORTH 
ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION; EUROPE -- DEFENSE; REUNIFICATION; MILITARY FORCE 
