-- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; LOS ANGELES -- FINANCES; HOUSING -- LOS 
ANGELES; AFFORDABLE HOUSING; SUBSIDIZED HOUSING; REAL ESTATE DEVELOPERS; FEES 
