<P>
Photo, GANG FIGHT: Chilton Alphonse, above, head of a South-Central Los Angeles 
anti-gang agency, says organizations like his are getting short-changed in 
government funding. LARRY BESSEL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
