<TEXT>
<P>
Gathers -- In a story on the legal issues involved in Hank Gathers' death in 
Thursday's editions, Stuart Biegel, who teaches education law at UCLA, was 
misquoted in his reference to a proposition on victims' rights that passed on 
the 1982 state ballot. He was referring to "the safe-schools portion of 
Proposition 8," not as written. 
</P>
