<TEXT>
<P>
Lepton, an undefeated 5 for 5 in 1990, will put her winning streak on the line 
when she tackles Tracy's Comet and six others in the $16,966 California 
Breeders Stakes for sophomore pacing fillies tonight at Los Alamitos. 
</P>
<P>
