Ronni and Black on Black. Tracy's Comet is one of only two fillies that have 
beaten Lepton with the other being Red Pepper, who surprised Lepton at Cal Expo 
in the summer. Tracy's Comet got her victory over Lepton on Dec. 22, with a 
lifetime best and track record mile of 1:57 3/5. 
